description: GIGAFICE develops web and mobile apps.
overview:
GIGAFICE develops enterprise level B2B, B2C Mobile and Web application. GIGAFICE provides a quality driven approach towards web and mobile development and provides complete services from requirement gathering till deployment. We also provide post development support and service.

Our team includes highly skilled engineers. We worked in almost all PHP frameworks such as Symfony, Yii, Kohana, Codeignitor, cakephp. Moreover, we worked in REST-APIs, Facebook SDK, Facebook open graph API, Twitter api, linkedin API, AWS(Amazon web services, EC2, S3), Jquery, JQuery Mobile, responsive layouts, CMS like Wordpress, Joomla, Drupal and ecommerce CMS like x-cart, prestashop, magento, oscommerce, woo-commerce etc.
